<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>My E-Portfolio</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg: #f9f7f4;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --ink: #1a1a18;
      --muted: #7a7a72;
      --accent: #2e6b4f;
      --accent-light: #e8f2ec;
      --border: #e4e2dd;
      --radius: 16px;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 72px 24px 56px;
      text-align: center;
      animation: fadeUp .8s ease both;
    }

    /* Profile photo */
    .avatar-wrap {
      position: relative;
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .avatar-wrap::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: -6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 2px solid var(--accent);
      opacity: .35;
    }
    .avatar {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      background: var(--accent-light);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 3px solid var(--surface);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    }
    .avatar svg {
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .hero .tagline {
      font-size: .95rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ── DIVIDER ── */
    .divider {
      width: 40px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--accent);
      margin: 32px auto;
      border-radius: 2px;
      opacity: .6;
    }

    /* ── VIDEO ── */
    .video-section {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto 16px;
      padding: 0 24px;
      animation: fadeUp .9s ease .15s both;
    }
    .video-label {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: .75rem;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .video-frame {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 16/9;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      background: var(--ink);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .video-frame video {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
    .video-placeholder {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
    }
    .video-placeholder svg { width: 48px; height: 48px; }
    .video-placeholder span { font-size: .85rem; letter-spacing: .04em; }
    .play-btn {
      position: absolute;
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform .2s, background .2s;
    }
    .play-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.08); background: rgba(255,255,255,.2); }
    .play-btn svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; fill: white; margin-left: 4px; }

    /* ── SUMMARY ── */
    .summary-section {
      max-width: 620px;
      margin: 0 auto 64px;
      padding: 0 24px;
      animation: fadeUp 1s ease .25s both;
    }
    .summary-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 32px 36px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .summary-card p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    .summary-card p strong {
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* ── TABS NAV ── */
    .tabs-nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 0 24px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      animation: fadeUp 1s ease .3s both;
    }
    .tab-btn {
      padding: 10px 28px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      background: transparent;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: .875rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--muted);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all .2s;
      letter-spacing: .02em;
    }
    .tab-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
    .tab-btn.active {
      background: var(--accent);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
    }

    /* ── SECTION CONTENT ── */
    .section-content {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px 80px;
      animation: fadeUp .5s ease both;
    }
    .section-content.hidden { display: none; }

    .section-title {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .section-subtitle {
      font-size: .875rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    /* Cards grid */
    .cards-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 24px;
      transition: box-shadow .2s, transform .2s;
      cursor: default;
    }
    .card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.07);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .card-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: .7rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent-light);
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .card h3 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .card p {
      font-size: .875rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    .card-meta {
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: .75rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      opacity: .7;
    }

    /* Gallery grid */
    .gallery-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .gallery-item {
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: var(--accent-light);
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform .2s;
    }
    .gallery-item:hover { transform: scale(1.02); }
    .gallery-item img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
    .gallery-placeholder {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      color: var(--accent);
      opacity: .5;
    }
    .gallery-placeholder svg { width: 32px; height: 32px; }
    .gallery-placeholder span { font-size: .75rem; letter-spacing: .04em; }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 48px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      animation: fadeUp .8s ease both;
    }
    .footer-label {
      font-size: .7rem;
      letter-spacing: .15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .social-links {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .social-link {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 100px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-size: .85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all .2s;
      background: var(--surface);
    }
    .social-link:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(46,107,79,.1);
    }
    .social-link svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .footer-copy {
      margin-top: 36px;
      font-size: .75rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      opacity: .6;
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .hero { padding: 48px 16px 40px; }
      .summary-card { padding: 24px 20px; }
      .tabs-nav { gap: 6px; }
      .tab-btn { padding: 9px 18px; font-size: .8rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="avatar-wrap">
      <div class="avatar">
        <!-- Replace with: <img src="your-photo.jpg" alt="Profile Photo"> -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
          <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 20c0-4 3.6-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h1>Your Name Here</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Your Title · Your Field</p>
  </section>

  <!-- VIDEO -->
  <div class="video-section">
    <p class="video-label">Introduction</p>
    <div class="video-frame">
      <!-- Replace with: <video src="your-video.mp4" controls poster="thumbnail.jpg"></video> -->
      <div class="video-placeholder">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
          <rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="3"/>
          <path d="M10 9l5 3-5 3V9z" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Your intro video goes here</span>
      </div>
      <div class="play-btn">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 4l13 8-13 8V4z"/></svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SUMMARY -->
  <div class="summary-section">
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm <strong>Your Name</strong> — a passionate professional dedicated to
        <strong>your area of expertise</strong>. I believe in continuous learning,
        creative problem-solving, and building meaningful work that makes a difference.
        Replace this text with your own personal summary and let the world know who you are.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="divider"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- TABS -->
  <nav class="tabs-nav">
    <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab('assignments', this)">Assignments</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('learnings', this)">Learnings</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('gallery', this)">Gallery</button>
  </nav>

  <!-- ASSIGNMENTS -->
  <div id="assignments" class="section-content">
    <h2 class="section-title">Assignments</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">A collection of my work and submitted assignments.</p>
    <div class="cards-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">Assignment 1</span>
        <h3>Project Title Here</h3>
        <p>Brief description of this assignment — what you did, what tools you used, and what you learned from it.</p>
        <p class="card-meta">Date · Subject / Course</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">Assignment 2</span>
        <h3>Project Title Here</h3>
        <p>Brief description of this assignment — what you did, what tools you used, and what you learned from it.</p>
        <p class="card-meta">Date · Subject / Course</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">Assignment 3</span>
        <h3>Project Title Here</h3>
        <p>Brief description of this assignment — what you did, what tools you used, and what you learned from it.</p>
        <p class="card-meta">Date · Subject / Course</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- LEARNINGS -->
  <div id="learnings" class="section-content hidden">
    <h2 class="section-title">Learnings</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Key takeaways, skills, and knowledge I've gained.</p>
    <div class="cards-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">Skill</span>
        <h3>Topic or Skill Name</h3>
        <p>What you learned, how you applied it, and why it was valuable to your growth or career.</p>
        <p class="card-meta">Month Year</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">Course</span>
        <h3>Course or Workshop Name</h3>
        <p>Summary of what this course covered and the most impactful lessons you took away from it.</p>
        <p class="card-meta">Month Year</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">Insight</span>
        <h3>Key Insight or Concept</h3>
        <p>A meaningful insight or concept that changed how you think about your field or approach your work.</p>
        <p class="card-meta">Month Year</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- GALLERY -->
  <div id="gallery" class="section-content hidden">
    <h2 class="section-title">Gallery</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Snapshots, moments, and visual memories.</p>
    <div class="gallery-grid">
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <!-- Replace with: <img src="photo1.jpg" alt="Description"> -->
        <div class="gallery-placeholder">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/>
